title: Ryan Russell from Nervous Energies/professional photographer
itunes:title: Ryan Russell from Nervous Energies/professional photographer
description:
I had the pleasure of speaking with Ryan Russell who is best known for his amazing photography as well as his awesomely fun music project, Nervous Energies. We spoke about his upbringing in the south, the continual battle of convincing parents you have a real job and relationships. Brought to you by Property of Zack (www.propertyofzack.com)
